  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK484">
<l>ñālaṅ karutiṉuṅ kaikūṭuṅ kālaṅ</l>
<l>karuti yiṭattāṟ ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though (a man) should meditate (the conquest of) the world, he may accomplish it if he acts in the right time, and at the right place.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
